snippet.title: Rebecca Zung
snippet.description:
Welcome to the world where you're negotiating your best life and excited to do it!  Slay your negotiation with that narcissist and take your life back!  

This channel is the only one that not only educates people on the behaviors of narcissists including the psychology of how they act in negotiations, but also is hosted by a Top 1% attorney in the United States, who offers actual proven strategies, tactics and step by step guidance on how to effectively create leverage so that you can shift the dynamic and create a fair resolution.   Rebecca has appeared on Extra!, Dr. Drew, NPR and in Forbes, Time, Newsweek and the Huffington Post, among many other outlets. Grab your free Crush My Negotiation Prep Sheet at www.winmynegotiation.com.  Find out more at https://www.rebeccazung.com.
